717408458887501.ofd" title="2.国家级零碳园区申报书大纲" _title="2.国家级零碳园区申报书大纲.ofd" oldsrc="/protect/P0202507/P020250717/P020250717408458887501.ofd">2.国家级零碳园区申报书大纲.ofd</a></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><a style="color:#0066cc;" appendix="true" data-appendix="true" needdownload="true" data-needdownload="true" otheroperation="false" data-otheroperation="false" href="./P020250717408459130750.ofd" title="3.国家级零碳园区建设指标体系（试行）.ofd" _title="3.国家级零碳园区建设指标体系（试行）.ofd" download="3.国家级零碳园区建设指标体系（试行）.ofd" oldsrc="/protect/P0202507/P020250717/P020250717408459130750.ofd">3.国家级零碳园区建设指标体系（试行）.ofd</a></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><a style="color:#0066cc;" appendix="true" data-appendix="true" needdownload="true" data-needdownload="true" otheroperation="false" data-otheroperation="false" href="./P020250717408459206726.ofd" title="4.零碳园区碳排放核算方法（试行）.ofd" _title="4.零碳园区碳排放核算方法（试行）.ofd" download="4.零碳园区碳排放核算方法（试行）.ofd" oldsrc="/protect/P0202507/P020250717/P020250717408459206726.ofd">4.零碳园区碳排放核算方法（试行）.ofd</a></p></div>
